Tiny Toy File System project folder description

bin: contains executables (contains .gitignore)
doc: contains documentation
dev: contains TTFS disks (contains .gitignore)
lib: contains library source files
obj: contains compiler-generated object files (contains .gitignore)
src: contains source files

Makefile: make command instruction tree
setup.sh: launches 'make' command
	  adds '$PWD/bin' folder to PATH environment variable
	  switches to 'dev' folder where disks located
	  > launch with 'source setup.sh'
